description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 MIN INTENSE FULL BODY HIIT WORKOUT I no repeat, no equipment I stronger together series DAY 5' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: An INTENSE Full Body Workout, that you can do without equipment and that will definitely get you sweating! Let's do this last STRONGER TOGETHER SERIES workout together! NO EXCUSES.

We are targeting the full body with this bodyweight workout.
